---
title: Asian Chicken Schnitzel & Garlic Rice with Saucy Veggies & Aioli
description: Give chicken schnitzel an Asian-style twist by seasoning it in a Southeast Asian inspired spice blend, plus a side of saucy veggies.
It's such a crowd-pleasing combo that you'd better prepare for repeat requests!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67598bc4daedc2bd1295a703-c600a507.jpeg
